Zapier,is,an,application,that,integrates,applications,together,Zapier,Status,is,a,dashboard,that,displays,the,current,status,of,every,API,that,Zapier,integrates,Zapier,Status,s,dashboard,also,allows,users,to,get,updates,via,multiple,channels,about,the,status,of,APIs,The,Zapier,Status,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,data,and,status,of,the,APIs,with,other,applications,The,main,API,method,is,retrieving,the,status,of,APIs